Package self.philbrown.AbLE

Interface Summary
ActivityListener Classes that wish to receive callbacks for activity lifecycle events should implement this interface, then call AbLEActivity.addListener(ActivityListener) to add itself as a callback receiver.
 

Class Summary
AbLEActivity This activity uses AbLE to create layouts from annotated java code.
AbLEUtil Provides shortcut methods for layouts, logging, etc
